{"tid":2438391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【推翻特朗普政策】拜登：讓外勞能與家人在「美國團聚」!","createTime":"2021-03-08T12:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T19:07:30.000Z","uid":318316,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"775febf9b5c4a121f7580c5aa9c36b309436bac8","tid":2438391,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:46:47.000Z","msg":"特朗普去年6月簽署宣言，大幅收緊簽發外勞簽證，凍結批出包括科網業吸納外國人才常用的H-1B工作簽證至年底，原因是要在武漢肺炎疫情下讓美國人優先就業。<br />\n<br />\n拜登在其宣言中反對特朗普提出的理據，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">認為特朗普的宣言妨礙美國公民及合法永久居民與家人在美國團聚，亦損害美國商界。</span></span></strong> <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210225/3YLWRLQZXNCIRN2RCTQOTWGOKA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210225%2F3YLWRLQZXNCIRN2RCTQOTWGOKA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=36f4daf2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210225%2F3YLWRLQZXNCIRN2RCTQOTWGOKA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=64f68815\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210225/3YLWRLQZXNCIRN2RCTQOTWGOKA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁似777既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180817/s00001/ce443542eee8536564aff85110510a8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180817%2Fs00001%2Fce443542eee8536564aff85110510a8e.jpg&h=d3cf6064&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"572e48f18c11637b2a13a0d1bf219fded06